{"word":"H7613 - שְׂאֵת - sᵉʼêth - seh-ayth' - Be accepted","slug":"H7613","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שְׂאֵת</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>sᵉʼêth"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>seh-ayth'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be accepted"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C2;&#x05D0;&#x05EA; - s&#x0301;<sup>e</sup>'e&#x0302;th</b> - <i>seh-ayth'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5375\">H5375</a>; an <i>elevation</i> or leprous scab; figuratively <i>elation</i> or cheerfulness; <i>exaltation</i> in rank or character: - be accepted, dignity, excellency, highness, raise up self, rising."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4853\">H4853</a>, <a href=\"#/H4856\">H4856</a>, <a href=\"#/H4858\">H4858</a>, <a href=\"#/H4864\">H4864</a>, <a href=\"#/H4984\">H4984</a>, <a href=\"#/H5375\">H5375</a>, <a href=\"#/H5379\">H5379</a>, <a href=\"#/H5385\">H5385</a>, <a href=\"#/H5387\">H5387</a>, <a href=\"#/H7721\">H7721</a>, <a href=\"#/H7863\">H7863</a>, <a href=\"#/H7865\">H7865</a>"}]}